applicationProcess.process_md:
**Unregistered applicant :**

1. All the applicant have to visit the official [website](https://cglabour.nic.in) Chhattisgarh Labour Department. 1. On the home page click on &quot;[Apply](https://cglabour.nic.in/Departments.aspx?id=4)&quot; under &quot;Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board&quot;.1. Enter the following details

   1. Select Group Name : &quot;Asangathit Marmakaar Mandal&quot;
   1. Select Service : &quot;Asangathit Shramik Panjikaran&quot;
   1. What do you want to do :  &quot;Aavedan&quot;
   1. Click next.

1. Check the eligibility criteria for registration in Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board and click next. 
1. Fill out the online &quot;Registration form&quot;.

<br>

<br>

**Already Registered Applicant :**

1. All the applicant have to visit the official [website](https://cglabour.nic.in) Chhattisgarh Labour Department. 1. On the home page click on &quot;[Apply](https://cglabour.nic.in/Departments.aspx?id=4)&quot; under &quot;Chhattisgarh Unorganized Workers State Social Security Board&quot;.1. Enter the following details

   1. Select Group Name : &quot;Asangathit Marmakaar Mandal&quot;
   1. Select Service : &quot;Yojana&quot;
   1. What do you want to do :  &quot;Aavedan&quot;
   1. Click next.

1. Select your district name and provide old/new registration number and click next.
1. Select the scheme name. 
1. Fill out the online with required details. 
1. Submit.

